<s> HTML (4.01) does not allow a script element directly inside a table .  </s>
<s> You'll need to either move the script inside a table cell ( th or td ), or have the script write the table element.  </s>
<s> Either of these changes needs the script to be modified, which is beyond Tidy's abilities.  </s>
